arts.ttl: Paul Rothrock, Stefan Frei lead Sounders to 1-0 victory over Real Salt Lake
arts.sum: Paul Rothrock scored an early goal and Stefan Frei made it stand up as the Seattle Sounders edged Real Salt Lake 1-0 on Saturday night. Frei finished with five saves for his eighth clean sheet in 25 starts this season for Seattle (14-9-10).
